- Short-term engineering tasks (2-4 weeks): tenant API for settings, frontend persistence, alert localization, Kenya formatting across dashboards.
- Compliance & legal review (1-2 weeks): finalize residency posture and customer-facing statements.
- Pilot publication: status page and support channel will be published on sign-off.

